    <example>
      <statement>
        <p>
          A <m>t</m>-distribution with 20 degrees of freedom is shown in the right panel of <xref ref="tDistDF3_and_20">Figure</xref>.
          Estimate the proportion of the distribution falling above 1.65.
        </p>
